serves: 65
---
- 4.5kg oats
- 120g cinnamon powder
- 20g cloves powder
- 30 g salt
- 32 apples
- 500ml apple vinegar
- 12L oat milk
- 300g sugar
- 750 g flaxseed meal
- 1,2kg Walnuts 
- 1.2kg Raisins/ Sultanien
- 2kg Honey
- 1200ml Pancake Syrup
- 2L UHT Cream
---
mix sugar salt cinnamon
add milk and vinegar
add apples diced
add flaxseed and oats

leave overnight
the rest is toppings

heat or not in the morning, the choice is yours